{"tid":637024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"獎金百萬　赴美受訓闖娛圈 ViuTV《全民造星》 招募男神交古仔揀蟀","createTime":"2018-04-21T12:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T16:54:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29fe6aad7387e6850bbadb4fb9707ff1a949ca50","tid":637024,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180421/20368036?_ga=2.14937910.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368036%3F_ga%3D2.14937910.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=8bf6bxIlOGmZ%2BMCXFMHmbpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3bd7cd2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368036%3F_ga%3D2.14937910.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=79ec2634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180421/20368036?_ga=2.14937910.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月21日 <br />\n<br />\n獎金百萬　赴美受訓闖娛圈<br />\nViuTV《全民造星》<br />\n招募男神交古仔揀蟀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/21ec3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2F21ec3p1.jpg&h=815c8906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■ViuTV將推出真人騷《全民造星》，勝出者可獲100萬現金獎及做明星。<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又有新搞作的ViuTV，將邀請全港娛樂公司合作推出真人騷《全民造星》，藉以發掘演藝界男神，勝出者除可獨得100萬現金獎外，更可以做明星晉身歌影視，有機會唱歌、拍戲和拍電視。ViuTV昨在facebook專頁上載宣傳短片，由劉嘉玲公開呼籲說：「如果你覺得自己又靚仔又唱得又跳得，咁你一定要參加ViuTV嘅《全民造星》呢個節目。」<br />\n<br />\n今次ViuTV打造男神節目，已落實邀得古天樂的天下一集團、周焯華（洗米華）的太陽娛樂文化、蕭定一的中國3D數碼娛樂、大國文化、環球唱片及星娛樂合作支持，而稍後將會有更多娛樂公司加入，齊齊發掘演藝界男神，說不定出爐影帝古天樂屆時都會參與做評判甚至在節目中亮相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/21ec3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2F21ec3p2.jpg&h=0fd38ee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■古天樂（左）和洗米華亦會支持。<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/21ec3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2F21ec3p3.jpg&h=c3798e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■ViuTV昨上載宣傳短片，劉嘉玲於片尾公開呼籲靚仔參賽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官網可報名<br />\n<br />\n參加者如果自認有演藝天份，只要是年滿18歲的男性及持有香港身份證的話，不論甚麼國籍和膚色都可以參加。《全民造星》由昨日起至下月12日晚上12時前可於ViuTV官網報名，又或於下月5日及13日參加ViuTV的公開招募活動。入圍參賽者需經過為期3個月的星級導師訓練，於節目內接受歌舞及各類演出考驗，而出線者更有機到美國進行集訓。<br />\n<br />\n記者昨致電ViuTV製作部副總裁金廣誠，問為何只選男神時，他說：「選完男神再選女神吖嘛。」那麼已是演藝界的男藝人可否參加比賽？金廣誠說：「只要冇合約喺身，以及自問聲色藝俱備就可以。」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：魯吉"},{"pid":"6ba95b8754b85ea51c267e56ebf8d0f8abe5cbd2","tid":637024,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"唉 要做冠軍了"},{"pid":"83c9f7dcf9f4cbe89313a7ba5e2418a47b995d07","tid":637024,"uid":90455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"太陽娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝贏個位好運"},{"pid":"0c8caf1020c279600a2536eebdc6ef74e17f7d05","tid":637024,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fef41cdf95dbb0e55597b63cb412b9822ff0506","tid":637024,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:54:22.000Z","msg":"100今時今日好少咋喎"}]}